Sample template for weekly status reports

Week of [month, day, year]

Significant Issues and PRs
  -Was something significant merged in the last week?
  -Was a PR submitted for a significant change?
  -Is there new/dynamic conversation happening about a PR that readers should look at?

Mailing List Discussions
  -Discussions happening that readers should look at (summarize and point to ML archives)

Community Updates
  -Is someone presenting a talk?
  -Noteworthy Kata news? (ie "Became an OCI member this week)
